==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Peles hair
<hw>Pe"le's hair</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[After a Hawaiian goddess
associated with the crater Kilauea.]</ety> <def>Glass threads or fibers
formed by the wind from bits blown from frothy lava or from the tips of
lava jets or from bits of liquid lava thrown into the air. It often
collects in thick masses resembling tow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Peleus</ent>⟦br⟧
